'''華倫天奴·羅斯''' ({{lang-it|Valentino Rossi}}，{{bd|1979年|2月16日|}})，是[[義大利|義大利]]退役職業摩托車賽車手，曾多次獲得[[世界電單車錦標賽|世界電單車錦標賽]]世界冠軍。1979年2月16日出生於意大利[[乌尔比诺|乌尔比诺]]，他的父親{{tsl|en|Graziano Rossi|格拉齊亞諾·羅西}}也曾是GP大獎賽的車手（1977-1982）。羅西目前隸屬{{tsl|en|Sepang Racing Team|山葉賽車|馬石油山葉賽車隊}}，從1996年加入世界電單車錦標賽，獲得全部級別9座世界冠軍，由於參賽以來成績優異有「小飛俠」與「猴王」的暱稱。羅西也是唯一參加過400場或更多大獎賽的賽車手。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/motorsport/50165800|title=Valentino Rossi: Italian says racing in 400th MotoGP is 'great achievement'|work=[[BBC體育|BBC體育]]|date=2019-10-24|accessdate=2020-10-17|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307235940/https://www.bbc.com/sport/motorsport/50165800|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他的整個職業生涯，包括他捍衛自己頭銜的歲月，都騎著46號賽車。

羅西於2000年畢業後，在2001年與[[本田技研工業|本田]]一起贏得了500cc級別比賽和鈴鹿8小時耐力賽，在2002年和2003年（也與本田一起）持續獲得冠軍，在離開本田加入[[山葉發動機|山葉]]之後，贏得了2004年和2005年的冠軍。在瓦倫西亞的最後一輪比賽中，他因失誤而失去了2006年的冠軍頭銜。2007年，羅西最終獲得第三名，然後在2008及2009年獲得冠軍。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/motorsport/motorbikes/8324552.stm |title = Rossi crowned world champion |author =  |date = 2009-10-25 |publisher = BBC體育 |language = en |accessdate = 2020-10-17 |quote = |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091028033143/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/motorsport/motorbikes/8324552.stm|archive-date= 2009-10-28}}</ref> 羅西在2010年賽季因腿部傷勢而無法進行比賽，2011年羅西離開山葉加入了[[杜卡迪|杜卡迪]]。<ref name="Rossi11">{{cite news|url=http://www.yamaha-racing.com/Racing/motogp/news/newsdetail.jsp?Component=tcm:78-383391&PageTitle=Yamaha%20and%20Valentino%20to%20part%20company%20at%20end%20of%202010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100819072352/http://www.yamaha-racing.com/Racing/motogp/news/newsdetail.jsp?Component=tcm:78-383391&PageTitle=Yamaha%20and%20Valentino%20to%20part%20company%20at%20end%20of%202010|archive-date= 2010-08-19|title=Yamaha and Valentino to part company at end of 2010|work=[[Yamaha_Motor_Racing|Yamaha Motor Racing]]|publisher=[[Yamaha_Motor_Company|Yamaha Motor Company]]|date= 2010-08-15|accessdate= 2020-10-17|language=en}}</ref><ref name="Ducati11">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/motorbikes/8886198.stm|title=Valentino Rossi to leave Yamaha for Ducati in 2011|work=BBC Sport|publisher=BBC|date=2010-08-15|accessdate=2020-10-17|language=en|archive-date=2017-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170902192609/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/motorsport/motorbikes/8886198.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref> 羅西在杜卡迪取代[[凯西·斯通纳|凯西·斯通纳]]，並在意大利車隊中度過了兩個賽季。

2012年證實他將在2013和2014賽季重新加入山葉。<ref name=backtoyam>{{cite news|url=http://www.motogp.com/en/news/2012/Rossi+back+to+Yamaha|title=Rossi heads back to Yamaha for 2013 on two-year contract|work=MotoGP.com|publisher=[[Dorna_Sports|Dorna Sports]]|date=2012-08-10|accessdate=2020-10-17|language=en|archive-date=2014-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140911002010/http://www.motogp.com/en/news/2012/Rossi+back+to+Yamaha|dead-url=no}}</ref> 重返山葉後，他在2013年獲得了積分榜的第四名，隨後在2014年、2015年和2016年連續三年獲得第二名的成績。羅西與山葉的合約將持續到2020賽季結束，屆時他將41歲。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.motorsport.com/motogp/news/rossi-signs-new-two-year-yamaha-deal-1014776/1396331/|title=Rossi signs new two-year Yamaha deal|last=Klein|first=Jamie|date=2018-03-15|accessdate=2020-10-17|website=Motorsport.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308165849/https://www.motorsport.com/motogp/news/rossi-signs-new-two-year-yamaha-deal-1014776/1396331/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 羅西將於2020年底離開山葉車隊，並於2020年9月26日確認他將在2021賽季加入馬來西亞國家石油SRT山葉賽車隊。<ref name="auto9">{{Cite web|url=https://www.motogp.com/en/news/2020/07/15/rossi-99-certain-he-will-ride-for-petronas-yamaha-in-2021/333289|title=Rossi "99% certain" he will ride for Petronas Yamaha in 2021|first=Dorna|last=Sports|website=www.motogp.com|accessdate=2020-10-17|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110014148/https://www.motogp.com/en/news/2020/07/15/rossi-99-certain-he-will-ride-for-petronas-yamaha-in-2021/333289|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.sportsv.net/articles/77844 |title = 【MotoGP】車手市場動態：Rossi正式宣佈將轉戰Petronas車隊 |author = Athrun |date = 2020-09-26 |publisher = 運動視界 |language = zh-tw |accessdate = 2020-10-18 |quote =  |archive-date = 2021-01-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210118200151/https://www.sportsv.net/articles/77844 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

2020年10月15日，罗西表示自己確診感染[[2019冠状病毒病|2019冠状病毒病]]。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-10-15|title=Valentino Rossi tests positive for Covid-19, will miss Aragon GP|url=https://www.eurosport.com/moto/valentino-rossi-tests-positive-for-covid-19-will-miss-aragon-gp_sto7951494/story.shtml|access-date=2020-10-15|website=Eurosport|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021133607/https://www.eurosport.com/moto/valentino-rossi-tests-positive-for-covid-19-will-miss-aragon-gp_sto7951494/story.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Staff|first=Reuters|date=2020-10-15|title=Rossi tests positive for COVID-19, to miss Aragon MotoGP|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-motor-motogp-aragon-rossi-idUKKBN2702LY|access-date=2020-10-17|archive-date=2021-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211203204557/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-motor-motogp-aragon-rossi-idUKKBN2702LY|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=MotoGP News: Rossi to miss Aragon GP with COVID-19|url=https://www.motorsport.com/motogp/news/rossi-miss-aragon-gp-positive-covid-19-test/4892343/?ic_source=home-page-widget&ic_medium=widget&ic_campaign=widget-1|access-date=2020-10-17|website=www.motorsport.com|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016235654/https://www.motorsport.com/motogp/news/rossi-miss-aragon-gp-positive-covid-19-test/4892343/?ic_source=home-page-widget&ic_medium=widget&ic_campaign=widget-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

